To compile and run this program:

1) Open a new project in Visual Studio.

2) Choose "Console App (.NET Core)" under C# in the New Project Dialog.

3) Name your project and click Create.

4) Replace the pre-filled code with the "Hello, World!" code provided.

5) To run the code, simply click on "Start Debugging" in the Debug menu, or press F5. 

You should see "Hello, World!" printed in your console.